---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TrustedBy from '../components/TrustedBy.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Catering Burnaby | Indian Catering for Weddings, Corporate & Events"
	description="Indian catering Burnaby for weddings, corporate offices, and private events. Halal, vegan, vegetarian. Delivery across Metrotown, Brentwood, and all Burnaby neighbourhoods."
	canonical="/catering-burnaby"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org","@type": "Service",
			"name": "Catering Burnaby",
			"provider": {"@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization"},
			"areaServed": {"@type": "City", "name": "Burnaby"},
			"serviceType": "Indian Catering"
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('/uploads/wedding-catering-burnaby-vancouver.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>Catering<br/>in <em>Burnaby</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Indian catering across Metrotown, Brentwood, Lougheed, Burnaby Mountain, and beyond. Award-winning since 2010.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/sula-catering-order/" class="btn btn-gold">Request Burnaby Catering</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TrustedBy />


	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<h2>Indian Catering for <em>Burnaby Events</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p>Burnaby is one of our largest catering markets. From Metrotown corporate offices to weddings at Hart House, from SFU campus events to private celebrations in Burnaby Heights, <a href="/" class="body-link">Sula Catering</a> delivers across every Burnaby neighbourhood. Our Commercial Drive kitchen is just minutes from the Burnaby border, which means hot food and on-time delivery, every time.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="/uploads/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond-office.webp" alt="Indian catering Burnaby" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">What We Cater in Burnaby</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Every <em>Burnaby Event</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="service-grid-v2">
				<a href="/weddings" class="service-card-v2 reveal">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-wedding-catering.webp" alt="Wedding catering Burnaby" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Burnaby Weddings</span>
							<h3>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>South Asian weddings at Hart House, Riverway Sport, Burnaby Mountain Clubhouse, and home celebrations.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Weddings →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-100">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/office-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Corporate catering Burnaby" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Metrotown · Brentwood</span>
							<h3>Corporate <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Office lunches and conference catering for Burnaby's tech corridors and Metrotown corporate towers.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Corporate →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-200">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/private-party-vancouver-catering.webp" alt="Private party Burnaby" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Burnaby Heights · Capitol Hill</span>
							<h3>Private <em>Parties</em></h3>
							<p>Birthdays, anniversaries, Diwali, housewarmings, across every Burnaby neighbourhood.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Private →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-300">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Cafe catering Burnaby" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Chai · Coffee · Pastries</span>
							<h3>Café <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Live masala chai bars and specialty coffee for Burnaby weddings, conferences, and brunches.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Café →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-plum pattern-mandala">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="/uploads/wedding-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Burnaby catering" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<h2>We Know <em>Burnaby</em></h2>
					<p>From Metrotown's corporate towers to the wedding venues along Deer Lake, from SFU to the Burnaby Heights residential streets, we've catered across every part of the city. Our delivery team knows the loading docks, the freight elevator quirks, and the parking realities.</p>
					<p>Sula's Commercial Drive flagship is right at the Burnaby border, which keeps delivery times short and food temperatures right. We also cater across <a href="/catering-vancouver" class="body-link">Vancouver</a>, <a href="/catering-richmond" class="body-link">Richmond</a>, and <a href="/catering-surrey" class="body-link">Surrey</a>.</p>
					<div class="experience-stats">
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">15min</div><div class="stat-label">From Kitchen</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">$5</div><div class="stat-label">Flat Delivery</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">2010</div><div class="stat-label">Established</div></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Common Questions</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Burnaby Catering <em>FAQs</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="faq-list">
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you cater Metrotown offices?</h3><p>Yes, daily corporate catering across Metrotown, Brentwood, and Lougheed corporate buildings.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>How fast is delivery to Burnaby?</h3><p>Our Commercial Drive kitchen is 15 minutes from most Burnaby neighbourhoods. Hot food, temperature-controlled.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you cater Burnaby wedding venues like Hart House?</h3><p>Yes, Hart House, Riverway, Burnaby Mountain Clubhouse, and home weddings across the city.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Is delivery to Burnaby extra?</h3><p>$5 flat delivery, no minimum order, same as our Vancouver pricing.</p></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>


	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<h2>Catering for <em>Burnaby</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us your venue, your guest count, your timeline.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/sula-catering-order/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
